Hey <%= @user.first_name %>, a new <%= @category.name %> activity is now available and waiting for you to join.  Here are the details...

<br />
<br />
<table class="email-activity-table">
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Category:</td>
		<td><%= @category.name %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Title:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.title %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Description:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.description %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Date:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.date_and_time.strftime("%a, %b %d") %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Time:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.date_and_time.strftime("%l:%M %p") %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Zipcode:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.zipcode %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Distance:</td>
		<td><%= "#{@activity.distance_to(@user).round(0)} miles" %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Place:</td>
		<td><%= @activity.where %></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class="bold">Organizer:</td>
		<td><%= @creator.username %></td>
	</tr>
</table>
<br />

<p>To view this activity and sign up, click <%= link_to "here", activity_url(@activity) %>.</p>

<p>You received this email because you are currently subscribing to the category "<%= @category.name %>" and are a member of the group "<%= @group.name %>".  If you no longer wish to receive emails in this category, please login and unsubscribe from this category.  If you no longer want to receive emails related to this group, please login and leave this group.</p>

<p>Please add 'IT'S ON!' to your contact list to ensure you receive these emails in the future.</p>
